long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Boost your Web Search Query with the Power of ChatGPT 🚀

Core Features:
On Google pages, Web Search Boost uses GPT to predict your search intent based on your input keywords. It then suggests relevant search terms for you. Just click to initiate a new, more focused search. 🤖🔍
More, in any page, when click the popup page, will detect the active window title, then provide some search plans.

To easy use, you can trigger the boosting session inside the google SERP page or manual trigger as need.

We are now support GPT3.5 (free and fast) or GPT4 (HQ, daily limit 5 times but slow) engine.

Welcome to the AI era - make Google smarter and your searches faster! 🌐✨
